          A quality match for the defensive purists- 17 shots on target and 12 goals. :-o . It really was a comical game to watch, particularly Cierzniak's er.. "efforts". He should really have 2 errors next to his name and a rating in minus figures. He should also have an assist for Sahin's goal. Credit where it's due. :-p . This is the record for most number of goals in a champions league game in case people didn't already know. The overall European cup record of 14 looked in danger when Nikolic scored but both teams had 8 minutes of doing nothing. Just pure laziness! Ha. There's no denying Dortmund look good in attack on their day but that defence is still too porous for me to believe they will take out a team with an equally good (or better) attack but a better defence, over 2 legs.
